reviewText: This is definitely a movie that isn't for everyone.  This is true for many of David Lynch movies or say a John Waters or Tarantino movie. You either like, love or hate this bizarre kind of movie or you appreciate it.  To me this movie and other movies by people I mentioned are works of art. As macabre and dark as they may be they are still great art!  I like "Wild At Heart" and "Blue Velvet" for the same reasons.
The Weirdest movie Ive ever seen but I Really liked it!
Surreal and interesting - held my attention.
